    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2>Embark on a challenging 2D platforming adventure with Ether, a skilled space mercenary, in a quest to retrieve vital data from an abandoned ship. Navigate through various hazards using your <u>Jump,</u> <u>Wall Jump</u>, <u>Dash</u>, and even a <u>Jetpack</u>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Hardcore Platforming Action</u>: Brace yourself for a tough platforming experience. Precision and timing are crucial and a little error will cost you your life! But no worries, you can retry as much as you'd like, and you'll learn through failure!<br><br></li><li><u>Engaging Story</u>: Unravel the story across four short, yet intense, chapters.<br><br></li><li><u>A Must For Completionists</u>: Retrieve 40 collectibles scattered in the different chapters and replay to beat your best time! We designed the achievements so reaching 100% completion is fun, and doesn't feel like a hassle!<br><br></li><li><u>Diverse Mechanisms</u>: Encounter and interact with a dozen unique mechanisms that will completely change the way you navigate the levels. Bumpers, zero-gravity pools, missile launchers...  And many more!</li></ul><br><strong>Prepare for a journey that will test your platforming skills and immerse you in a thrilling adventure with Ether. Can you retrieve the data and uncover the secrets of the abandoned ship?</strong>",
